          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780393068474" href="/book/show/7237456-packing-for-mars">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30307187-glitterbomb?shelf=5-star">5-star</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30307187-glitterbomb?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30307187-glitterbomb?shelf=owned">owned</a>, 
